{"tid":102779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp挑戰友誼、情侶　將增加「朋友定位」功能！","createTime":"2017-01-31T23:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T16:58:21.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaf2a6edc1d31bff310a2898aece5fab94b541c","tid":102779,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:48:10.000Z","msg":"科技<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp挑戰友誼、情侶　將增加「朋友定位」功能！<br />\n<br />\n15小時前&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=ab3b5c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a>】為令功能更加全面，WhatsApp過去陸續加入一些備受爭議的特性，像是雙藍勾以及上線時間等等。這些功能出發點絕對是好的，但對於一些友誼或情侶之間缺乏信任的人來講卻是大災難。而這個災難不止於此，因為即將還會加入一個「朋友定位」功能，相信必定又會帶來新一輪口水戰。<br />\n<br />\n據WABetaInfo消息指出，WhatsApp在近日推出的iOS及Android版的最新測試版本（2.17.3.28 iOS<br />\n<br />\n2.16.399+ Android）中，被揭暗中加入一個類似 Find My Friend 的「Location」（位置）的新功能。此功能在測試版本中預設是隱藏的，預計還未計劃正真的推出時間。<br />\nWhatsApp預設允許使用者分享自己位置的時間，像是1分鐘、2分鐘、5分鐘或者是永久。然後，你可以選擇將位置與某一些朋友分享，而該朋友以後就可以透過 WhatsApp 來查看你身處的位置。"},{"pid":"f2e10f22d694d82dba46d286b238d4890bdb5aa9","tid":102779,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"D人識自己打卡架啦"},{"pid":"00a744812b096f57dca54fda06b71441c77e3e81","tid":102779,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:57:16.000Z","msg":"fakegps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cb0716f3f890fdc9ef25a0c1dd54fa0525e6b4","tid":102779,"uid":31172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fakegps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfake去半山扮有錢佬食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2d3437827059cdf37d5f7fc1feb30b1fd17a0e","tid":102779,"uid":31172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0